            <li>Arguably unconstitutional - no explicit constitutional authority for fiat currency</li>
            <li>No longer backed by or redeemable for gold since 1971</li>
            <li>Monetary debasement (theft) is required for the credit-based economy to function</li>
            <li>Total supply is both unknown and unknowable</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="sp-beneficiary">Beneficiary &#8594; <strong>The government</strong></div>
