      <div class="govt-note"><p><strong>The critical distinction:</strong> Fiat inflation is not some unfortunate event beyond anyone's control, like the weather. It is an intentional, structural mechanism &#8212; the silent transfer of economic energy from the people who earned it to the government (who printed it out of thin air - no "work" involved). With gold and Bitcoin, any new supply goes to those who did the work. With fiat, it goes to those who hold the printing press; every dollar they print is a dollar stolen from all existing holders of dollars, including you.</p></div>
